# Project Overview : Solar Asset Dataset
# What is the dataset?
# A full year (Jan–Dec 2024) of real solar plant SCADA data recorded every 5 minutes. It covers 10 inverters (INV_01 to INV_10), giving 1,051,200 rows and 25 columns. Each row is one inverter at one 5-minute timestamp.
